des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control the KKT.Control app. After you have connected Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our app KKT.Control from the app market, and then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our app KKT.Control and change the appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon or from the Google Play Store or iOS App Store, and connect Echo to the "Alexa" app;
(4) Search for the KKT.Control Smart skill in the Alexa app's skill category;
(5) Activate the KKT.Control Smart skill and you will be navigated to the login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete the link;
(7) Now all settings are completed. Try speaking to Echo to control your devices:
Examples:
- Alexa, turn on the light.
- Alexa, turn off the light.
- Alexa, dim the light.
- Alexa, brighten the light.
- Alexa, set the light to blue.
